<body>
  <div style="margin-left:20px;text-align:center">
    <span><h3 style="display:inline-block;font-weight:100;font-size:45px;margin-top:2px;">Password Strength Widget</h3>   
    <span class="label label-primary" id="howitworks" data-toggle="popover" data-trigger="hover" style="cursor:pointer">?
